HEADWORD: Proteles
<hw>Pro"te*les</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A South Africa genus of Carnivora, allied to the
hyenas, but smaller and having weaker jaws and teeth. It includes the
aard-wolf.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

